<td>~</td>
<td><i>thought</i></td>
<td><span title="Representation in the International Phonetic Alphabet (IPA)" class="IPA">[θɔːt]</span></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><i>catch</i></td>
<td><span title="Representation in the International Phonetic Alphabet (IPA)" class="IPA">[kætʃ]</span></td>
<td>~</td>
<td><i>caught</i></td>
<td><span title="Representation in the International Phonetic Alphabet (IPA)" class="IPA">[kɔːt]</span></td>
</tr>
</table>
</dd>
</dl>
<ul>
<li>Vowel change between base and past/<i>-en</i> forms and <i>-(e)n</i> suffixation:</li>
</ul>
<dl>
<dd>
<table>
<tr>
<td><i>break</i></td>
