</dd>
</dl>
<ul>
<li>Vowel changes in base, past, &amp; <i>-en</i> forms with <i>-(e)n</i> suffixation:</li>
</ul>
<dl>
<dd>
<table>
<tr>
<td><i>drive</i></td>
<td><span title="Representation in the International Phonetic Alphabet (IPA)" class="IPA">[drаɪv]</span></td>
<td>~</td>
<td><i>drove</i></td>
<td><span title="Representation in the International Phonetic Alphabet (IPA)" class="IPA">[droʊv]</span></td>
<td>~</td>
<td><i>driven</i></td>
<td><span title="Representation in the International Phonetic Alphabet (IPA)" class="IPA">[drɪvən]</span> (<i>drive</i> + <i>-(e)n</i>)</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><i>fly</i></td>
<td><span title="Representation in the International Phonetic Alphabet (IPA)" class="IPA">[flаɪ]</span></td>
<td>~</td>
<td><i>flew</i></td>
<td><span title="Representation in the International Phonetic Alphabet (IPA)" class="IPA">[fluː]</span></td>
<td>~</td>
<td><i>flown</i></td>
